videos.description: Josiah-Jordan James pulls up to knock down a contested 3-pointer to beat the halftime buzzer and give Tennessee a 27-24 lead over South Carolina.
videos.headline: Josiah-Jordan James drains a 3 to beat halftime buzzer for Vols
